Download Arduino ide
Then open the preferences from file
put the following link In Managing the titles of additional panels
https://dl.espressif.com/dl/package_esp32_index.json

open the boards manger from tools, board: "Arduino Uno " 
search for ESP32 in the searching box then install
Connect the ESP32 with your devise with a USB 

choose WEMOS D1 MINI ESP32 from tools, board: "Arduino Uno ", ESP32 Arduino.

choose COM3 from tools , port:"COM3 " 
